parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of entries to return on each page. Valid values: 1 to 100. Default value: 10.

parameters.name: MemberIds
parameters.description: A list of IDs of members managed by the IPAM trusted service.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The token that is used to retrieve the next page of results. Valid values:

- If **NextToken** is empty, no more results are available.

- If **NextToken** has a value, the value is the token for the next query.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the hosted region of the IPAM. Call the [DescribeRegions](~~448570~~) operation to get the region ID.
